text: Cameo Kirby is a 1930 American drama movie directed by Irving Cummings and based on the 1909 play of the same name by Booth Tarkington and Harry Leon Wilson. It stars J. Harold Murray, Norma Terris, Douglas Gilmore, Robert Edeson, Myrna Loy and was distributed by 20th Century Fox. It is a lost movie. ==Other websites== * Category:1930 drama movies Category:1930s American drama movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Irving Cummings
